{"tid":2278952,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔請食飯等於孤寒?約幾個女仔等於花心?","createTime":"2020-11-09T12:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T23:17:19.000Z","uid":249170,"like":3,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"20da16f88d16d9a9a838d51df284596a484a9c40","tid":2278952,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"女仔揀男仔要知道一個男仔靠唔靠得住好多時要睇佢d小行為黎作判斷<br />\n<br />\n<ins>第一次食飯唔揀高級餐廳</ins> = 唔會在意另一半感受,自私狗,做事只顧自己<br />\n<br />\n<ins>唔悉心打扮,唔著西裝</ins> = 唔識尊重人,唔顧儀容,間屋一定好亂<br />\n<br />\n<ins>唔主動派餐具，幫女仔夾食物</ins> = 唔識照顧人,溫室長大兒童,會當老婆工人咁洗<br />\n<br />\n<ins>唔請食飯</ins> = 孤寒,小家,斤斤計較,狗西,唔會養妻活兒<br />\n<br />\n<ins>唔送女仔返屋企</ins> = 有難既時候就自己走先,唔會理身邊既人安全<br />\n<br />\n<ins>除左約你之外仲會約其他女仔</ins> = 花心,濫交, 容易有第三者,派帽比你,有機會有性病<br />\n<br />\n<ins>佢追你,你拒絕佢就唔再追你</ins> = 花心,冇上進心，容易放棄，唔洗指意佢日後會升官發財<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇，求各位巴絲指教，謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdde46222fc870f41f200020f6941d8384e937c","tid":2278952,"uid":98385,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"宜家啲基佬咁多要求"},{"pid":"7182068d67e212070a2aad432cf0e1245869cb3b","tid":2278952,"uid":9392,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"你搞分化都高章啲啦"},{"pid":"cc5e4b7336c97d796475b29304eca97cbaa9ac39","tid":2278952,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"你 = 臭西"},{"pid":"97989b2b4e95bd6d8c9dcbb3872e7f05eb94508c","tid":2278952,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"on撚9"},{"pid":"6b13d4ae3e34e77e3552c6b529792674ef304d04","tid":2278952,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci